OL,7,FThe Trump administration views him not
OL,8,Fas a disciple of peace and
OL,9,Funderstanding, but as a trouble-maker
OL,10,Fwhom they are determined to kick out
OL,11,Fof the country.
OL,13,FHe is one of a growing number of high-
OL,14,Fprofile students who have been
OL,15,Farrested, often by plain-clothed
OL,16,Fofficers, and detained at immigration
OL,17,Fcentres hundreds of miles from where
OL,18,Fthey are studying.
