OL,7,FHe is determined not to be silenced,
OL,8,Feven as his legal battle to stay in
OL,9,Fthe United States continues to play
OL,10,Fout. He is also very adamant that the
OL,11,Fprotests were in no way anti-semitic
OL,12,For pro-Hamas.
OL,14,FWhen I asked about some Jewish
