OL,7,FMahdawi has been a green card holder
OL,8,Ffor the past 10 years and is due to
OL,9,Ffinish his undergraduate degree in
OL,10,Fphilosophy at Columbia University in
OL,11,FNew York this month.
OL,13,FThe 34-year-old, who was born and
OL,14,Fraised in a refugee camp in the West
OL,15,FBank, became a prominent organiser of
OL,16,Fpro-Palestinian demonstrations on
OL,17,Fcampus, speaking out about Israel's
OL,18,Fmilitary campaign in Gaza.
