OL,7,FHe co-founded 'Dar: the Palestinian
OL,8,FStudent Society' at Columbia alongside
OL,9,FMahmoud Khalil, after the October 7th,
OL,10,F2023, Hamas attack on Israel. Khalil
OL,11,Fis also facing deportation proceedings
OL,12,Fand is currently in detention at a
OL,13,FLouisiana prison.
OL,15,FAccording to submissions made by
OL,16,FMahdawi's lawyers, he took a step back
OL,17,Ffrom protest organising in March 2024,
OL,18,Fbefore the student encampments at
OL,19,FColumbia University began.
